  <prefix>§</prefix>
  <num>19-2116</num>
  <heading proof="needed">Office of trust director.</heading>
  <para>
    <num>(a)</num>
    <text>Unless the terms of a trust provide otherwise, the rules applicable to a trustee apply to a trust director regarding the following matters:</text>
    <para>
      <num>(1)</num>
      <text>Acceptance under <cite path="§19-1307.01">§ 19-1307.01</cite>;</text>
    </para>
    <para>
      <num>(2)</num>
      <text>Giving of bond to secure performance under <cite path="§19-1307.02">§ 19-1307.02</cite>;</text>
    </para>
    <para>
      <num>(3)</num>
      <text>Reasonable compensation under <cite path="§19-1307.08">§ 19-1307.08</cite>;</text>
    </para>
    <para>
      <num>(4)</num>
      <text>Resignation under <cite path="§19-1307.05">§ 19-1307.05</cite>;</text>
    </para>
    <para>
      <num>(5)</num>
      <text>Removal under <cite path="§19-1307.06">§ 19-1307.06</cite>; and</text>
    </para>
    <para>
      <num>(6)</num>
      <text>Vacancy and appointment of successor under <cite path="§19-1307.04">§ 19-1307.04</cite>.</text>
    </para>
  </para>
